<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>688</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a, zhǔ a, tīng shuō nǐ kuài huí lái le.
 wǒ duō me gāo xìng a, yě duō me hài pà.
 yīn wèi wǒ méi yǒu zūn xíng hǎo nǐ de zhǐ yì,
 yě méi yǒu kàn shǒu hǎo nǐ de jiā.
 zhǔ a, wǒ zhēn gǎn xiè nǐ, gěi wǒ huǐ gǎi de jī huì.
 ràng wǒ jīn tiān néng gòu bǎ ēn ēn yuàn yuàn dōu fàng xià.
 yīn yīn qín qín shí shí zài zài
 qù shōu gē qù mù yǎng. bǎ làng zi dài huí fù jiā.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ a tīng shuō nǐ kuài huí lái le 迦南688</title>
</song>